Prophetic Ravings", "set": "EMN", "type_line": "Enchantment — Aura", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["R"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/f/9/f9e58861-a548-4344-a37b-1c5764b144d9.jpg?1782711853", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/f/9/f9e58861-a548-4344-a37b-1c5764b144d9.jpg?1782711853", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/emn/139/prophetic-ravings?utm_source=api", "local": "img/prophesy/69af7bff-fb8c-4f59-88a1-6bfa87ba400a.jpg"}, {"id": "620f3851-493d-496e-880a-4a9dee074e79", "name": "Shadow Prophecy", "set": "DMU", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/b/b/bb078448-9e9f-4994-8aff-7e7c4fb62efc.jpg?1782700490", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/b/b/bb078448-9e9f-4994-8aff-7e7c4fb62efc.jpg?1782700490", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/dmu/105/shadow-prophecy?utm_source=api", "local": "img/prophesy/620f3851-493d-496e-880a-4a9dee074e79.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Bogwater Lumaret", "set": "SOS", "html": "&quot;You will hear rumors that licking lumarets grants <mark>prophetic</mark> visions. That is untrue. Please refrain from licking the lumarets.&quot;\n—Witherbloom student handbook", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/a/7a42f51a-3377-47bb-b6fb-c0515bf1dcfb.jpg?1782682884"}, {"card": "Steam Augury", "set": "C15", "html": "Keranos is a fickle god, delivering punishment as readily as <mark>prophecy</mark>.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/b/3bb510af-2cc7-4992-aeef-556e8a63f146.jpg?1782712305"}, {"card": "Piety", "set": "4ED", "html": "&quot;Whoever obeys God and His <mark>Prophet</mark>, fears God and does his duty to Him, will surely find success.&quot;\n—*The Qur&#x27;an, 24:52*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/d/4/d4942a9f-6b8f-438b-a2ea-366228038ed8.jpg?1782721942"}, {"card": "Green Sun's Zenith", "set": "2X2", "html": "As the green sun crowned, Phyrexian <mark>prophecies</mark> glowed on the Tree of Tales.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/0/70291c7b-a86f-4466-8502-c28765a89b2a.jpg?1782737868"}, {"card": "Omenspeaker", "set": "CMR", "html": "Her <mark>prophecies</mark> amaze her even as she speaks them.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/b/1b635abe-ad7e-44b8-b3fe-6e365db87c29.jpg?1782706045"}, {"card": "Fiery Emancipation", "set": "M21", "html": "&quot;One day the mountain&#x27;s fire will rise up to burn away our chains and end this age of oppression.&quot;\n—*The Molten <mark>Prophecy</mark>*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/b/0b12e4b7-2c45-4795-94d3-901f89b8f290.jpg?1782706926"}, {"card": "Duskana, the Rage Mother", "set": "MKC", "html": "&quot;A pale bear shall herald the rise of the old gods.&quot;\n—Gruul <mark>prophecy</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/1/31fa9d47-43d6-44b5-ab86-fc94a83eac26.jpg?1782694215"}, {"card": "Sigiled Starfish", "set": "JMP", "html": "Kruphix hid the most dire <mark>prophecies</mark> about humankind where humans would never find them and tritons wouldn&#x27;t care to read them.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/a/7a1a93c3-8561-4c65-bea8-a9c3a898a48c.jpg?1782706668"}, {"card": "Horizon Chimera", "set": "C16", "html": "&quot;Do not try to make sense of the chimera. Impossibility is its habitat.&quot;\n—Kydele, <mark>prophet</mark> of Kruphix", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/0/7022506d-8685-41e0-bd1a-2c27c964128b.jpg?1782711384"}, {"card": "Serra", "set": "PVAN", "html": "Named for a benevolent goddess at birth, Serra fulfilled the <mark>prophecy</mark> of that goddess&#x27;s coming. As a planeswalker, she embodies white mana and helps whole civilizations develop while both directly and indirectly inspiring countless individuals to be steadfast and strong in the service of light.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/d/cd55ffd2-cb98-4c66-a79d-0da5e927360c.jpg?1782755481"}, {"card": "Witches' Eye", "set": "THS", "html": "The price of <mark>prophecy</mark> is a vacant eye socket.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/d/6d989daa-78eb-4120-81b5-7866a7b04590.jpg?1782713715"}, {"card": "Sidar Jabari", "set": "VMA", "html": "&quot;<mark>Prophecy</mark> is whatever one makes of it, but destiny cannot be changed.&quot;\n—Sidar Jabari", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/6/c6d7c16b-27f2-4608-bb79-c2edb86abdef.jpg?1782751457"}, {"card": "Oracle", "set": "PVAN", "html": "Known simply by her title, Oracle uses her gift of <mark>prophecy</mark> to aid her people. She believes Gerrard to be the *Korvecdal*, the one who will unite the people of Rath against Volrath&#x27;s tyranny. Her only doubt is whether she will be strong enough to guide him to his destiny.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/f/af5cc745-7072-4f7f-94eb-c7670cb498ff.jpg?1782755492"}, {"card": "Dragonstalker", "set": "SCG", "html": "&quot;When the skies are filled with flames, the brave shall step forward to quench them.&quot;\n—Order <mark>prophecy</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/8/58017ff1-74d2-4be2-976a-8dff53e16150.jpg?1782719010"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Fire Prophecy", "set": "IKO", "html": "Fire <mark>Prophecy</mark> deals 3 damage to target creature. You may put a card from your hand on the bottom of your library. If you do, draw a card."}, {"card": "Prophetic Bolt", "set": "2X2", "html": "<mark>Prophetic</mark> Bolt deals 4 damage to any target. Look at the top four cards of your library. Put one of those cards into your hand and the rest on the bottom of your library in any order."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/a/7a42f51a-3377-47bb-b6fb-c0515bf1dcfb.jpg?1782682884", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/7/a/7a42f51a-3377-47bb-b6fb-c0515bf1dcfb.jpg?1782682884", "card": "Bogwater Lumaret"}}